modName: Jk's Towns and Riverwood Log Home Compatibility - DELETED
summary: This esp makes it so Jk's Towns and the Riverwood log home play well with each other
descriptionHtml:
This is just a simple mod to fix the docks where these two mods conflict
I am using

JK's Skyrim
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61035

Jk's Skyrim Towns Only is the one I used in this

Log Home in Riverwood No Loading Screen
https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92778

using 2.0 of this mod for this

All you have to do is replace your jk's Skyrim Towns esp with the one I provided and there should be no more conflicts

I have also made it so dragons can land on the log home and on the bank of the river

There is also a small extension of the dock to add a small fishing area

I have uploaded a video showing it in game:
https://youtu.be/BR8z9spkvw8
author: Chaodyn
